title: Radwanska wins Tianjin Open to qualify for WTA Finals
text: Radwanska wins Tianjin Open to qualify for WTA Finals Sunday, 18 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) TIANJIN, China (AP) " Agnieszka Radwanska defeated Danka Kovinic 6-1, 6-2 in less than an hour to win the Tianjin Open title on Sunday and clinch a spot in the WTA Finals in Singapore.The second-seeded Radwanska broke Kovinic five...
